window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Seven strangers are invited to compete to win a clifftop mansion. The rules are simple: each contestant must have at least one hand in contact with one part of the house at all times. The last one to take their hand off, wins the house.</p> <p>After 36 hours, a contestant is murdered. Soon they start to realise that it may not be the last person to leave the house that wins it, it may be the last person alive.</p> <p>From the bestselling author of <i>Find Us</i> and <i>Everyone in My Family Has Killed Someone</i> comes a locked room mystery where the door is open, but no-one wants to walk through it.</p>"; 
